WEBVTT

00:00.154 --> 00:02.054
Harvey:
Previously on <i>Suits...</i>

00:02.055 --> 00:04.390
This is Harvey Specter.
He's our best closer.

00:04.457 --> 00:05.858
Recruiting, your interviews
are set up for tomorrow.

00:05.926 --> 00:07.326
I work better
alone anyway.

00:07.394 --> 00:08.661
We only hire
from Harvard,

00:08.728 --> 00:10.496
and you haven't even gone
to any law school.

00:10.563 --> 00:11.697
What if I told you
that I consume knowledge

00:11.765 --> 00:12.998
like no one you've ever met,

00:13.066 --> 00:14.199
and I've actually passed
the bar.

00:14.267 --> 00:16.468
Okay, hotshot,
fire up this laptop.

00:16.536 --> 00:17.836
Stock option backdating.

00:17.904 --> 00:20.172
Under IRC section 409a.

00:20.240 --> 00:21.507
You forgot
about Sarbanes-Oxley.

00:21.574 --> 00:23.008
Impressive, but you're sitting
at a computer.

00:23.076 --> 00:26.278
Playing Hearts.
If you want to beat me,

00:26.346 --> 00:27.513
you're going to have to do it
as something else.

00:27.580 --> 00:28.781
How can you know all that?

00:28.848 --> 00:30.316
Once I read something,
I understand it.

00:30.383 --> 00:32.718
And once I understand it,

00:32.786 --> 00:33.886
I never forget it.

00:33.954 --> 00:35.421
I'm inclined
to give you a shot.

00:35.488 --> 00:37.256
But if they find out I lied
about you going to Harvard,

00:37.324 --> 00:39.625
they'll take away my license.
You what?

00:39.693 --> 00:41.126
Not now, Donna.

00:41.194 --> 00:42.695
The Harvard law school
alumni database.

00:42.762 --> 00:44.863
I'm not saying
you won't get caught,

00:44.931 --> 00:45.831
but it won't be because
your story doesn't check.

00:45.899 --> 00:47.066
I'm Rachel Zane.

00:47.133 --> 00:48.801
I'll be giving you
your orientation.

00:48.868 --> 00:50.102
I love you.

00:50.170 --> 00:51.770
Harvey's
your commanding officer.

00:51.838 --> 00:53.706
However, Louis Litt,
he oversees all associates,

00:53.773 --> 00:54.840
so you'll also answer to him.

00:54.908 --> 00:56.475
Welcome to Pearson Hardman.

00:56.543 --> 00:57.843
How many more chances
are you going to give that kid?

00:57.911 --> 00:59.912
I didn't realize
we were keeping score.

00:59.980 --> 01:01.680
But if that's the case, I still
think he's coming out ahead.

01:01.748 --> 01:04.083
This habit of you empathizing
with every client--

01:04.150 --> 01:05.617
it's not getting
you anywhere.

01:05.685 --> 01:07.653
You need to deal in information
that can hold up.

01:07.721 --> 01:09.722
- That's what a real lawyer does.
- Why?

01:09.789 --> 01:11.190
- What?
- Fire me.

01:11.257 --> 01:12.291
Why would you do that to me?

01:12.359 --> 01:15.828
Life is this.
I like this.

01:15.895 --> 01:18.530
It's tough to have a
relationship with a first-year,

01:18.598 --> 01:20.199
or any year.

01:20.266 --> 01:23.035
You're playing with me,
and you know it.

01:23.103 --> 01:25.237
You kept flirting with me long
after you started dating her.

01:25.305 --> 01:27.106
How about you find yourself
some other paralegal?

01:27.173 --> 01:29.174
Because, as far
as I'm concerned, we're done.

01:29.242 --> 01:31.844
How did you two meet?
I dated his best friend.

01:31.911 --> 01:33.245
You always liked her.

01:33.313 --> 01:34.813
Nothing happened
until Trevor and I were done.

01:34.881 --> 01:37.182
- Never?
- Well, we did kiss once.

01:37.250 --> 01:38.817
- I can't.
- It's a real firm.

01:38.885 --> 01:40.686
But you can't tell
anyone ever.

01:40.754 --> 01:41.987
This guy is not your friend,

01:42.055 --> 01:43.155
he is an anchor
dragging you down.

01:43.223 --> 01:44.223
Get rid of him.

01:44.290 --> 01:46.091
He's my oldest friend.

01:46.159 --> 01:47.326
I know you're seeing Jenny,

01:47.394 --> 01:51.330
but I can't stop thinking
about the kiss.

01:51.398 --> 01:52.464
I'm Trevor Evans.

01:52.532 --> 01:53.832
I'm a friend of Mike Ross.
Yes.

01:53.900 --> 01:55.167
I wish I didn't have
to do this.

01:55.235 --> 01:56.668
There's something you need
to know about him,

01:56.736 --> 01:58.704
something Harvey Specter
hasn't told you.

02:00.000 --> 02:06.074
